ms.gle/hDfcr3wCsprrvnC37</a><br />\n<br />\n【最後4日】全民票選十八區區議會主席與發言人－民主統戰部<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1800922\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1800922</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/phk5doO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fphk5doO.jpg&h=40b71bc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n投票： <a href=\"https://forms.gle/hDfcr3wCsprrvnC37\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FhDfcr3wCsprrvnC37&d=OJrKX0dn%2BAqYJaSYBqJK9%2FY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=4d7cbcce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/hDfcr3wCsprrvnC37</a><br />\n快啲入黎投票呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d52fa95803666edd00b49a175bf76c83677c4b7","tid":1802432,"uid":313341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T12:55:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"02b9832cd8bca4bdf570af2a456b894cfea844dd","tid":1802432,"uid":2974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T12:56:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">候任荃灣區議員陳劍琴亦有出席，她指「黃色經濟圈」難以覆蓋長者</span><br />\n<br />\n又係喎，去咁多黃店都係後生1x-4x歲多，再老d或者銀髮族就算知個概念都未必咁投入，有咩計仔？例如區議員蛇齋餅粽crossover黃店？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fd0e1994cac573df75637e140792d57a7c78639","tid":1802432,"uid":51583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"06f04cd4626c7636d853410c2bb258859c2cc28c","tid":1802432,"uid":46911,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b53e5c4bdeda4276164052595f397ee912ae9a7d","tid":1802432,"uid":234116,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T12:41:49.000Z","msg":"講起荃灣就諗起串燒保單嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T12:45:04.000Z","msg":"訓左冇睇<br />\n阿串燒保事頭婆約左蘋果做訪問未？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T13:08:45.000Z","msg":"約左<br />\n已經篤爆左<br />\n之前D客幫襯佢既錢就追唔到<br />\n捐既錢都拎得到唔少<br />\n蝕左幾皮就拎唔返當係幾個老闆私人蝕比佢<br />\n舖頭已經關門大吉避風頭<br />\nBTW荃灣呢批黃店好多都出錢出力做好多野<br />\n雪糕舖 茶店 冰室等等其實出過唔少錢"},{"pid":"0e764f8ab8d84d6c7761dd0531cc9c494b7f78c9","tid":1802432,"uid":51583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T13:09:42.000Z","msg":"長者真係冇計<br />\n佢地生活習慣始終圍繞酒樓/街市<br />\n消費唔會多<br />\n好難改變"},{"pid":"f1d3391d3e3e02a2ce973b63adf953d47dd12923","tid":1802432,"uid":1219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6d52fa95803666edd00b49a175bf76c83677c4b7","tid":1802432,"uid":313341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T12:55:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T13:09:53.000Z","msg":"依個扑街一定要生 can 一級級上，醫好再生另一種！"},{"pid":"b8bdd9f8ad051a1309152fb8717fd3963f180308","tid":1802432,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"02b9832cd8bca4bdf570af2a456b894cfea844dd","tid":1802432,"uid":2974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T12:56:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">候任荃灣區議員陳劍琴亦有出席，她指「黃色經濟圈」難以覆蓋長者</span><br />\n<br />\n又係喎，去咁多黃店都係後生1x-4x歲多，再老d或者銀髮族就算知個概念都未必咁投入，有咩計仔？例如區議員蛇齋餅粽crossover黃店？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T13:13:51.000Z","msg":"你張議員傳單有張減兩蚊既優惠券<br />\n盲既阿婆都會仆住去排隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e373e9684b3ae42b35da7ebb060fd41b6c2031fe","tid":1802432,"uid":78519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T13:14:52.000Z","msg":"推"}]}